query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('confidence-interval',
'cosmology',
'cross-validation',
'electric-circuits',
'energy',
'gravity',
'hilbert-space',
'metric-tensor',
'neural-networks',
'normal-distribution',
'regression',
'self-study',
'symmetry',
't-test')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics',
'stats')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Constituent',
'Enlightened',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Favorite Question',
'Good Answer',
'Necromancer',
'Promoter',
'Revival',
'Self-Learner')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
